{"tid":1283463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【電腦資訊】有沒有人用Mac 但冇聽過 FileVault","createTime":"2019-07-03T21:13:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T22:11:59.000Z","uid":271068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"727f8d826c5ba0ec1285597f09095d996efec516","tid":1283463,"uid":271068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T21:13:39.000Z","msg":"今時今日雖然好少人還用laptop , 但成部機咁先進，有啲功能，真係唔係預設值就開咗。<br />\n<br />\n要入setting 效：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://macuknow.com/2019/01/24/1368/不敢用-filevault-保護你的資訊安全？新的觀念讓你放心用/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmacuknow.com%2F2019%2F01%2F24%2F1368%2F%E4%B8%8D%E6%95%A2%E7%94%A8-filevault-%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%EF%BC%9F%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%80%E5%BF%B5%E8%AE%93%E4%BD%A0%E6%94%BE%E5%BF%83%E7%94%A8%2F&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O69osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=c26e8be6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://macuknow.com/2019/01/24/1368/不敢用-filevault-保護你的資訊安全？新的觀念讓你放心用/</a>"},{"pid":"114ea7a94224d049d492d73ea03ca6f754688d60","tid":1283463,"uid":271068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T21:14:42.000Z","msg":"FileVault 是幫你把整顆硬碟加密的一個加密功能，如果你對你資料比較重視，蠻建議你開啟這個功能。不過，很多人對他有一點誤解，覺得他好像會把電腦變得很安全，但又會拖累速度，讓電腦像烏龜一樣。又怕自己忘記密碼之後拿不回資料，所以大多人都是不敢開啟這功能的<br />\n<br />\n迷思1：忘記密碼很嚴重，資料全部掰掰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">迷思2：會拖累電腦速度，乾脆不要開。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n嗯，說對也不完全對，這有點是過往的的技術資訊套用在最新的電腦上，實際上現在的 FileVault 已經可以讓你無縫使用，自己都忘記有開這功能，直到某天你的電腦被偷，才會慶幸好險有開。"},{"pid":"68bb75486206c2fdf9d190c25e556b5ae3dd1592","tid":1283463,"uid":258973,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T21:20:16.000Z","msg":"Day 0用Mac 已經開咗<br />\n好似由有T1定T2 晶片嘅Mac 開始，硬碟加密由粒T1/T2晶片做，唔會對CPU效能有影響"},{"pid":"cf21b21f2a6a66e93b9e99c98bb294f6589ef731","tid":1283463,"uid":271068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T21:33:30.000Z","msg":"用window 的人，建議將重要檔案放在外置HD.<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要加密</span></span><br />\n<br />\n**但不建議加密C Drive, 好易自己都開唔返。<br />\n<br />\n***重要野不要用window <br />\n常清 browser history. <br />\nChrome 不要save password. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://isvincent.pixnet.net/blog/post/39352859-windows-8-使用bitlocker加密隨身碟\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fisvincent.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F39352859-windows-8-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8bitlocker%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86%E9%9A%A8%E8%BA%AB%E7%A2%9F&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O69osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=611a299b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://isvincent.pixnet.net/blog/post/39352859-windows-8-使用bitlocker加密隨身碟</a>"},{"pid":"47f67825f341bcce9c43ef9fce37937ffd600938","tid":1283463,"uid":258973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf21b21f2a6a66e93b9e99c98bb294f6589ef731","tid":1283463,"uid":271068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T21:33:30.000Z","msg":"用window 的人，建議將重要檔案放在外置HD.<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要加密</span></span><br />\n<br />\n**但不建議加密C Drive, 好易自己都開唔返。<br />\n<br />\n***重要野不要用window <br />\n常清 browser history. <br />\nChrome 不要save password. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://isvincent.pixnet.net/blog/post/39352859-windows-8-使用bitlocker加密隨身碟\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fisvincent.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F39352859-windows-8-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8bitlocker%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86%E9%9A%A8%E8%BA%AB%E7%A2%9F&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O69osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=611a299b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://isvincent.pixnet.net/blog/post/39352859-windows-8-使用bitlocker加密隨身碟</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T21:48:18.000Z","msg":"Bitlocker 真係吹鳩脹，Win7 到而家都未擺得上大台<br />\n<br />\n以前好似聽過，換咗機解密唔返之類嘅嘢(好似係)"},{"pid":"cbd7bd223c65d6ba124def59742bff2e37aeb255","tid":1283463,"uid":271068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47f67825f341bcce9c43ef9fce37937ffd600938","t